

1.creating sqoop job:
---------------------
sqoop job --create sqoop_delta_job -- import \
--option-file 'D:/Big_Data/Sqoop/code/sqoop-connet-import'
--table order_delta \
--target-dir 'user/data/order' \
--fields-terminated by ',' \
--as-textfile \
--check-column order \
--incremental append \
-m 1;


2. list of sqoop job:
======================

sqoop job --list

2. execute sqoop job:
======================

sqoop job --exec sqoop_delta_job 


3.delete sqoop job:
====================


4. show sqoop paramenters:
==========================
sqoop job --show sqoop_delta_job